sequenceDiagram
    actor U as Free User
    participant FE as React<br/>AlertDetailPage
    participant API as DRF<br/>AlertDetailView
    participant SER as AlertDetailSerializer
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    U->>FE: Click alert row in AlertListPage
    FE->>API: GET /api/alerts/{alert_id}/
    API->>DB: Alert.objects.get(pk=alert_id)
    DB-->>API: Alert instance
    API->>SER: AlertDetailSerializer(alert)
    SER-->>API: Full alert data with metadata
    API-->>FE: 200 OK {alert detail}
    FE-->>U: Render alert detail panel with InfoRow components
